Text.string: Great news, recruit! I've got one last Clapslist ad for you.
Thanks for answering my summons, recruit! Follow me!
She freaking SHOT me! WHY is that everyone's first reaction to the sound of my voice?!
Keep up your whinging out there and it's gon' happen again!
We're just here to dance! And I always get my money! Go talk to her, recruit. She probably won't shoot you!
I said get the hell outta here. There won't be no dancing today.

Y'all are too late, okay? Posted that ad years ago. I'd been living alone for a while, and wanted someone to take me out dancin'. But no one came. It ain't easy to find a dancin' partner around Pandora.
But y'all are just too damn late, okay? So you ain't gettin' your money.
Whaaat?! Wheels are just fine for dancing, Baby! In fact, they're even BETTER!
Oh! But this first part will require charisma and charm! And since you have none of those, just watch the master! Me, Claptrap!
Shhhhhhh. Just let our wheels do the talking.
Oh, you sweet, one-wheeled angel. Thank you. I—I really needed that. Next time, don't take so long to come see me, okay?
Agghhh!
This is the last one!
Meet me on Pandora! Some dummy is gonna pay us a butt-load of money just to go dancing! Suckerrr. And since MY wheel isn't for rent, you'd better bring your dancin' shoes!
Don't look at me like that, I'm doing all the wheel-work here.
Hey, I'm charming as shit! Anyone who says otherwise is getting a brick through their window!
Who says I don't have charm and charisma? I'll crush their skulls!
Charm is for those too weak to earn respect.
Charisma? Charm? Those are my middle names!||I have a lot of middle names.
This house has a ramp? Nice! Screw stairs!
Come on, Vault Hunter. We want that money, so show her what you can do!
You call that dancing?
Is that the best you can do?
I feel like you're not giving it your all.
If you want that money, then dance, recruit! Dance!
Wow, that was TERRIBLE! Maybe I was wrong.
No. You don't understand. Look at me. I can't dance anymore. Not on these wheels.
No. You should just go.
Recruit, hit the music!
Okayyy... let's go!
Perfect! And awayyy we go!
You're not getting rid of me that easy! We're just getting started!
Recruit, over here!

Wow! I had a REAL emotional moment back there! I feel like a new bot! After all that, I can't take her money—but here, have some of mine! I'll see you back on Sanctuary. Now GET LOST, I've got more dancin' to do!
Our client's name is Baby. Let's see if she's home! All you have to do is dance with her, then I'll get all the money! And I'll pay you what you deserve, which is hardly anything!
Heyyy, Baby! Hello? Baby? Hnh. No answer. Let's try the doorbell like the refined and civilized folk we are!
Go away! Didn't you see the sign? It says, “I'll shoot you.” And it ain't kiddin'!
We're here for that ad you posted, after a slight delay. So come on out and dance—
